2.找出兩波形的0.7_0.3¶

In [3]:
#
V=1.8
V_7=V*0.7#1.26
V_3=V*0.3#0.54
d=0.05
d2=0.1
#
def f_level(x):
    global V,V_7,V_3,d,d2,pre_level
    level=np.nan
    #0
    if abs(x-0)<d:
        level=pre_level='0'
    #1.8        
    if abs(x-V)<d:
        level=pre_level='1.8'
    #0.7    
    if abs(x-V_7)<d2:
        #
        if pre_level=='1.8' or pre_level=='-7':
            level=pre_level='-7'           
        #
        if pre_level=='+3' or pre_level=='+7':
            level=pre_level='+7'                                    
    #0.3
    if abs(x-V_3)<d2:
        #
        if pre_level=='-7' or pre_level=='-3':
            level=pre_level='-3'           
        #
        if pre_level=='0' or pre_level=='+3':
            level=pre_level='+3'  
    #
    return level
#
def f_gnum(x):
    global pre_level,pre_gnum
    gnum=np.nan
    if x in ['-7','-3','+3','+7']:        
        if pd.isnull(pre_gnum):
            pre_gnum=1
        else:
            if x!=pre_level:            
                pre_gnum+=1
        #
        pre_level=x
        gnum=pre_gnum
    #
    return gnum
#SDA_________
pre_level=np.nan
df['sda_level']=df['SDA'].map(f_level)
pre_level=pre_gnum=np.nan
df['sda_gnum'] =df['sda_level'].map(f_gnum)
#SCL_________
pre_level=np.nan
df['scl_level']=df['SCL'].map(f_level)
pre_level=pre_gnum=np.nan
df['scl_gnum'] =df['scl_level'].map(f_gnum)
#0,1.8,0.3,0.7nan
df['SDA_73']=df['SDA'].where(pd.notnull(df['sda_level']),np.nan)
df['SCL_73']=df['SCL'].where(pd.notnull(df['scl_level']),np.nan)
#

SDA求最接近0.7,0.3準位的唯一時間¶

In [15]:
cond=pd.notnull(df.sda_gnum)
df_sda=df[['T','SDA','sda_level','sda_gnum']][cond]
df_sda.count()
#
def sda_find73(mydf):
    global V_7,V_3
    sda=mydf['SDA']
    sda_level=mydf['sda_level'].values[0]
    #
    if sda_level in ['+7','-7']:
        mydf['delta']=abs(sda-V_7)
    if sda_level in ['+3','-3']:
        mydf['delta']=abs(sda-V_3)   
    #
    return mydf.sort_values(by='delta',ascending=True)[0:1]
#
df_sda.groupby('sda_gnum').apply(sda_find73).head(10)
